<!DOCTYPE html>


<html data-theme="light" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 20 - Rutina Semanal</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-corporate-blue {
            background-color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-red {
            border-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-blue {
            border-color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-light-gray {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
        }
        .routine-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .routine-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<header class="w-full h-24 flex items-end justify-between px-12 pb-4 relative z-10" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 1024px; height: 96px; box-sizing: border-box;">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-corporate-red"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-corporate-red"></span>
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Plan de Acción</p>
</div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-corporate-blue">Tu rutina semanal</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-end">
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">20</p>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-1 px-16 py-8 flex flex-col justify-center relative" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 1024px; height: 672px; box-sizing: border-box;">
<div class="absolute right-0 top-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-50 rounded-full -z-10 opacity-40"></div>
<div class="absolute left-10 bottom-10 w-48 h-48 bg-red-50 rounded-full -z-10 opacity-40"></div>
<div class="mb-6 w-full flex justify-between items-end">
<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl" style="max-width: 560px;">
                    Implementa este sistema para gestionar tus redes en <span class="font-bold text-corporate-red">2-3 horas totales</span> por semana.
                </p>
<div class="bg-blue-50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-blue-100" style="min-width: 240px;">
<p class="text-corporate-blue font-semibold"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock mr-2"></i>Tiempo total estimado: 180 min</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-6 h-full pb-8">
<div class="col-span-2 routine-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-blue transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
<div class="bg-blue-100 text-corporate-blue px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-bold uppercase">Lunes</div>
<div class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock mr-1"></i>30 min</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue">
<i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">Generar Calendario</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 pl-14">Define los temas y pilares de la semana.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-span-2 routine-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
<div class="bg-red-100 text-corporate-red px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-bold uppercase">Lunes</div>
<div class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock mr-1"></i>60-90 min</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red">
<i class="fa-solid fa-pen-nib"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">Crear 5-7 Posts</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 pl-14">Redacción, diseño simple y búsqueda de recursos.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-span-2 routine-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-blue transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
<div class="bg-blue-100 text-corporate-blue px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-bold uppercase">Martes</div>
<div class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock mr-1"></i>30 min</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue">
<i class="fa-solid fa-upload"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">Programar Todo</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 pl-14">Sube todo a Metricool o Meta Business Suite.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-span-3 routine-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-blue transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 bg-gray-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 text-xl group-hover:text-corporate-blue group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
<i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
<span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold uppercase">Diario</span>
<span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock mr-1"></i>10 min</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Responder Comentarios</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Mantén el engagement activo y conecta.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-span-3 routine-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 bg-gray-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 text-xl group-hover:text-corporate-red group-hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
<i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
<span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold uppercase">Viernes</span>
<span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock mr-1"></i>15 min</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Revisar Analytics</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Analiza qué funcionó y ajusta para la próxima.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-20" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">21 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-22" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>


